sourcesContent:
let searchInputStyle = {
  width: "calc(65.9vw - 28px)",
  height: "30px",
  outlineWidth: "0px",
  boxSizing: "border-box",
  fontSize: "17px",
}

let listContainerStyle = {
  display: "inline-block",
  minWidth: "100%",
  marginTop: "10px",
  height: "88.8vh", 
  overflowY: "scroll",
  zIndex: -1,
}

let searchTypeOther = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  width: "98px",
  height: "27px",
  marginRight: "2px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none",
  fontWeight: "bold",
  color: "black"
}

let searchTypeOtherHighlight = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  width: "94px",
  height: "25px",
  border: "2px solid #07405b",
  marginRight: "2px",
  paddingTop: "1px",
  textAlign: "center",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none",
  fontWeight: "bold",
  color: "white"
}

let searchTypeMain = {
  ...searchTypeOther, borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 0px",
}

let searchTypeMainHighlight = {
  ...searchTypeOtherHighlight, borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 0px"
}


export {
  searchInputStyle,
  listContainerStyle,
  searchTypeOther,
  searchTypeOtherHighlight,
  searchTypeMain,
  searchTypeMainHighlight,
}
